    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<h1><code>IntStream::boxed</code></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/IntStream.html#boxed()\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>IntStream::boxed</code></a> turns an <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/IntStream.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>IntStream</code></a> into a <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Stream&lt;Integer&gt;</code></a>, which you can then <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html#collect(java.util.stream.Collector)\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>collect</code></a> into a <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/util/List.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>List</code></a>:</p>\n<pre><code>theIntStream.boxed().collect(Collectors.toList())\n</code></pre>\n<p>The <code>boxed</code> method converts the <code>int</code> primitive values of an <code>IntStream</code> into a stream of <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/11/docs/api/java.base/java/lang/Integer.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>Integer</code></a> objects. The word <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Object_type_(object-oriented_programming)#Boxing\" rel=\"noreferrer\">&quot;boxing&quot;</a> names the <code>int</code> ⬌ <code>Integer</code> conversion process. See <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/tutorial/java/data/autoboxing.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Oracle Tutorial</a>.</p>\n<h2>Java 16 and later</h2>\n<p>Java 16 brought the shorter <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/16/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html#toList()\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><code>toList</code></a> method. Produces an <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/16/docs/api/java.base/java/util/List.html#unmodifiable\" rel=\"noreferrer\">unmodifiable list</a>. Discussed <a href=\"https://todd.ginsberg.com/post/java-16/stream-tolist/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>\n<pre><code>theIntStream.boxed().toList() \n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
