    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use primitive collections available in <a href=\"http://www.eclipse.org/collections/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Eclipse Collections</a> and avoid boxing.</p>\n\n<pre><code>MutableIntList list = \n    IntStream.range(1, 5)\n    .collect(IntArrayList::new, MutableIntList::add, MutableIntList::addAll);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note: I am a contributor to Eclipse Collections.</p>\n"
