    "body" : "<p>You could also use mapToObj() on a Stream, which takes an IntFunction and returns an object-valued Stream consisting of the results of applying the given function to the elements of this stream.</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Integer&gt; intList = myIntStream.mapToObj(i-&gt;i).collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n"
