    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Find the folowing example of finding square of each int element using Java 8 :-</p>\n\n<pre><code>IntStream ints = Arrays.stream(new int[] {1,2,3,4,5});       \nList&lt;Integer&gt; intsList = ints.map(x-&gt; x*x)\n          .collect(ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt;::new, ArrayList::add, ArrayList::addAll);\n</code></pre>\n"
