  "title" : "How do I convert a Java 8 IntStream to a List?",
  "body" : "<p>I'm looking at the docs for the <code>IntStream</code>, and I see an <code>toArray</code> method, but no way to go directly to a <code>List&lt;Integer&gt;</code></p>\n\n<p>Surely there is a way to convert a <code>Stream</code> to a <code>List</code>?</p>\n"
